# Smart SQL Assistant

An AI-powered app that converts English questions into SQL, executes them in MySQL, and shows results in a table.

## Features
- Ask database questions in English
- Auto-generate optimized SQL using Gemini AI
- Secure MySQL execution
- View results in tabular format

## Tech Stack
Streamlit, LangChain, MySQL, Google Gemini, PyMySQL, Pandas

